[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has a minimum opening hand with no extra features to brag about.
So after NORTH's Jacoby 2NT bid he merely signs off at 4\S.

NORTH would have cooperated if SOUTH had made a slam try, but she doesn't have enough 
to initiate the investigation herself.}

